  "notes": "Source is the genuine SBSeg 2018 site captured by the Wayback Machine (2019-01-24); the live sbseg2018.imd.ufrn.br domain and the sbseg-sbc.github.io clone now serve unrelated content (SBSeg 2019/2021), so they were not usable. The clone https://sbseg-sbc.github.io/sbseg2018/ returned no relevant committee links. Members listed here are the main-track Technical Program Committee, taken from the section 'Comitê de Programa - ST - Sessão Técnica'. The page lists ST committee member names WITHOUT affiliations; affiliations filled in here were taken from the same 2018 page where the same person appears with an institution in another committee block (program committee of CTD/WGID/MC, coordination roles, etc.). Empty inst means no affiliation was given on this page. 65 members. Anderson Rocha (UNICAMP) and Marcos Simplício (USP) are the ST committee coordinators (chairs) and also appear in the member list. Other committees (CTD, WGID, WFC, Minicurso, WTICG, local organizing) were excluded as they are not the main-track PC."
